							"paragraphStyle" : {
								"__type" : "textStyle"
							},
							"string" : "In GT we approach the user interface as a language. The user inferace is not fixed, but composable using operators like views and lepiter pages. When integrating LLM suport into GT we do not want a chat chat standalone and isolated from the rest of the environment, we want it to be another operator that can be freely used."
						},
