							},
							"paragraphStyle" : {
								"__type" : "textStyle"
							},
							"string" : "And the same as humans use views and lepiter pages to understand a system, we want also LLM agents to use them.  Views and lepiter pages become skills that LLM agents can levreage to reason about our systems."
